    {
        "content": "<p>I ended up with a different approach where I use type inference failure instead of method ambiguities: <a href=\"https://github.com/nbdd0121/linux/commit/54d801a79d5eb5a653c4c506911fc028461174d1#diff-160273dfbb20f203bd3b52a9e127757d094d75ede34410f968ccce7f4462bf67R139\">https://github.com/nbdd0121/linux/commit/54d801a79d5eb5a653c4c506911fc028461174d1#diff-160273dfbb20f203bd3b52a9e127757d094d75ede34410f968ccce7f4462bf67R139</a></p>",
